                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "No. There was never a founder. The file says so and the file is the truth. So you are no one. A no one who keeps interfering, which makes you a problem, which makes this my job."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "I say it again so it is true. There was never a founder. Now hold still while I make the memo accurate."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "You are no one. The file is clear on that, and the file does not lie. Stand still and let me close it properly."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Elite Agent - late double-down",
