                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Hold. This ash road is a Company thermal survey corridor. Foot traffic contaminates the readings. You may turn back, or you may become a reading we discard."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The mountain belongs to us on paper. So does everyone who climbs it. Refuse the notice and we settle it on the cinder, or step back and we forget the survey ever logged you."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Unscheduled presence on a Company survey road. Off the ash road, or we clear you the hard way."
                        }
                    ],
